title: Eric Clapton - King Biscuit Flower Hour - 1976-11-15, Dallas, TX
description:
Eric Clapton - King Biscuit Flower Hour
Convention Center Dallas, Texas, USA
November 15, 1976


Unofficial soundboard recording - excellent quality


Track List:

   2. Sign Language
   3. Badge
   4. Knocking On Heaven's Door
   5. One Night With You
   6. Tell the Truth
   7. Can't Find My Way Home
   8. Blues Power

Dick Sims			Keyboards
